title: John List - Family Man To Americas Most Wanted? 18 Year Case
description:
Hi Friends!

Today I wanted to talk about John List and wow, no words. We need to bring back Americas Most Wanted. I don't have TV so if its still on, forgive me, but dang if it wasn’t for that show , who knows what would’ve happened ! 

 I love and appreciate you guys so much, please be safe out there! Love love love you.
xo
Bailey Sarian
